    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 87.</p><p>Tier I: Fingers of Toth</p><p>Arcane Precision. You have a +3 bonus to spell attack rolls. Additionally, your critical range for spell attacks is increased by 1.</p><p>Quickened Cantrip. When you cast a spell of 1st level or higher, you can cast a cantrip with a casting time of 1 action or 1 bonus action as part of the same action used to cast the leveled spell.</p></div>",
